426
00:18:37,500 --> 00:18:39,458
This boy must be really
rich or something.

427
00:18:40,791 --> 00:18:41,958
[CLERK]
Your glasses are ready for

428
00:18:42,041 --> 00:18:43,666
you to wear, young mistress.

429
00:18:43,750 --> 00:18:45,083
That's fast!

430
00:18:45,166 --> 00:18:47,333
Courtesy transportation
is waiting for you outside, sir.

431
00:18:47,416 --> 00:18:48,458
What d'you mean?

432
00:18:48,541 --> 00:18:50,500
[VOICES] Limousine!

433
00:18:50,583 --> 00:18:52,500
All for you.
Just hop right on in.

434
00:18:55,291 --> 00:18:57,833
At some point, things
got a bit out of hand, huh?

435
00:18:57,916 --> 00:18:59,708
Yeah, just a little.

436
00:18:59,791 --> 00:19:01,125
[CLASS REP] I wish
I could go shopping with

437
00:19:01,208 --> 00:19:03,583
Nagasumi like
I did with this boy.

438
00:19:04,166 --> 00:19:05,166
[Class Rep sighs]

439
00:19:05,250 --> 00:19:08,083
Is there something
bothering you?

440
00:19:08,166 --> 00:19:09,625
Maybe...

441
00:19:09,708 --> 00:19:12,125
I will try telling the person
I like how I feel about him.

442
00:19:12,208 --> 00:19:14,875
Life is brief.
Fall in love, maidens.

443
00:19:14,958 --> 00:19:16,458
Life really is brief.

444
00:19:16,541 --> 00:19:19,083
We never really know for sure,
so you have to hang in there.

445
00:19:19,166 --> 00:19:20,666
I'm on your side.

446
00:19:20,750 --> 00:19:22,291
Thank you so much.

447
00:19:22,375 --> 00:19:23,958
It's all thanks to
you I finally gained

448
00:19:24,041 --> 00:19:25,958
the courage to face my feelings.

449
00:19:26,041 --> 00:19:28,666
Oh, hey, why don't you give
your new glasses a test drive?

450
00:19:28,750 --> 00:19:32,625
Yeah. That's a good idea.
And really, thank you again.

451
00:19:32,708 --> 00:19:34,416
They look really good!

452
00:19:37,958 --> 00:19:40,000
[CLASS REP] No!

453
00:19:40,083 --> 00:19:41,333
[CLASS REP] Let me out!

454
00:19:41,416 --> 00:19:42,958
[Class Rep yelps]

455
00:19:43,041 --> 00:19:44,416
You've gotta be kidding!

456
00:19:44,500 --> 00:19:47,208
What was Nagasumi
doing there? Crap!

457
00:19:47,291 --> 00:19:49,000
Are you all right?

458
00:19:49,083 --> 00:19:50,500
[CLASS REP] No!

459
00:19:50,583 --> 00:19:52,125
[NAGASUMI]
Tell me what's the matter!

460
00:19:52,208 --> 00:19:53,791
[CLASS REP] Stay away from me!

461
00:19:53,875 --> 00:19:56,166
[NAGASUMI] Please just
tell me what's wrong!

462
00:19:58,958 --> 00:20:01,375
[CLASS REP]
Uh, what's happening?

463
00:20:01,458 --> 00:20:03,916
I can't take this. I can't!

464
00:20:04,541 --> 00:20:05,625
[NAGASUMI] Um, uh...

465
00:20:05,708 --> 00:20:08,375
What happened?
I don't understand.

466
00:20:09,333 --> 00:20:11,666
[CLASS REP THINKS] Why has
Nagasumi been acting so distant,

467
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:14,166
like he just met
me or something?

468
00:20:14,708 --> 00:20:17,000
Could it be he doesn't
recognize me?

469
00:20:17,666 --> 00:20:19,708
[CLASS REP THINKS]
I can work with this!

470
00:20:20,708 --> 00:20:22,333
Keep him thinking
I'm someone else!

471
00:20:22,416 --> 00:20:24,041
I'm sorry. Please don't
worry about it!

472
00:20:24,125 --> 00:20:26,000
This was just one
of my fits, that's all.

473
00:20:26,083 --> 00:20:27,208
[NAGASUMI] Uh, fits?

474
00:20:27,291 --> 00:20:28,416
Uh. Oh... I just remembered
something urgent

475
00:20:28,500 --> 00:20:29,458
I have to take care of.

476
00:20:29,541 --> 00:20:30,708
Well I need to get going.
That I do.

477
00:20:30,791 --> 00:20:32,250
[NAGASUMI]
"That I do?"

478
00:20:33,875 --> 00:20:36,083
Okay then.
Well, good luck.

