with that, right?

482
00:20:43,083 --> 00:20:44,125
You're rooting for me then?

483
00:20:44,208 --> 00:20:45,500
[NAGASUMI] Yep!

484
00:20:45,583 --> 00:20:49,125
Life is brief, fall in love,
that's what you told me.

485
00:20:49,208 --> 00:20:51,041
Did you really mean it?

486
00:20:51,125 --> 00:20:52,875
[NAGASUMI] Of course

487
00:20:52,958 --> 00:20:55,125
'Kay. I'll do the best
that I know how to.

488
00:20:55,208 --> 00:20:56,875
Hold on.
Before you go,

489
00:20:56,958 --> 00:20:58,250
will you please
tell me your name?

490
00:20:58,333 --> 00:21:00,125
